Third-Party Dependencies
-----------------------
This project may include or depend on the following third-party libraries, each with their own license:

1. PlatformIO (https://platformio.org/) - Used for firmware development
   License: Apache 2.0

2. M5Stack Libraries (https://github.com/m5stack/M5Stack-Cardputer) - Hardware abstraction
   License: MIT or Apache 2.0 (depending on component)

3. FastLED (https://github.com/FastLED/FastLED) - LED control library
   License: MIT

4. ArduinoJson (https://github.com/bblanchon/ArduinoJson) - JSON parsing
   License: MIT

5. Python MCP (Model Context Protocol) - For plugin communication
   License: Apache 2.0

6. Mistral AI Vibe CLI dependencies - For plugin integration
   License: Varies (see individual packages)

7. WiFiClientSecure - ESP32 WiFi with TLS
   License: Apache 2.0

8. HTTPClient - ESP32 HTTP client
   License: Apache 2.0

For complete dependency information, see:
- firmware/platformio.ini (firmware dependencies)
- plugin/requirements.txt (Python dependencies)
- pyproject.toml (Python package dependencies)

